\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $\rho$
\end_inset

 written in the same basis, i.e., 
\begin_inset Formula $\rho=\tensor*[_{\mathscr{O}}]{\sum}{_{i=0}^{d-1}}\tensor*[_{\mathscr{O}}]{\sum}{_{i=0}^{d-1}}r_{ij}\ket{\psi_{i}}\bra{\psi_{j}}$
\end_inset

